{"prompt": "Build a sleek website for a premium automotive dealership. The design should prominently display a true black.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Motors - Premium Automotive</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #000000; /* True Black */\n            --secondary-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark Charcoal */\n            --accent-color: #d4af37; /* Gold */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --subtle-text-color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n            font-weight: 400;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 80vh;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552414691-1c71931b344b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #c19c30;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .featured-cars, .about-us, .contact {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .featured-cars h2, .about-us h2, .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .car-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .car-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .car-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .car-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .car-card-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .car-card-content h3 {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .car-card-content p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-us-content {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .about-us-content p {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact input, .contact textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact input::placeholder, .contact textarea::placeholder {\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--subtle-text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">APEX MOTORS</div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#featured\">Featured</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Experience Automotive Excellence</h1>\n            <p>Discover a curated selection of the world's most prestigious automobiles. Uncompromising luxury, unparalleled performance.</p>\n            <a href=\"#featured\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Collection</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"featured\" class=\"featured-cars\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Vehicles</h2>\n            <div class=\"car-grid\">\n                <div class=\"car-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317654-833824421b4a?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80\" alt=\"Luxury Sedan\">\n                    <div class=\"car-card-content\">\n                        <h3>The Sovereign Sedan</h3>\n                        <p>Timeless design meets cutting-edge technology for an unparalleled driving experience.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"car-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517527102020-4709e1467975?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80\" alt=\"Supercar\">\n                    <div class=\"car-card-content\">\n                        <h3>The Velocity GT</h3>\n                        <p>Exhilarating performance and breathtaking aesthetics. Redefine speed.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"car-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612818173907-326a282c6f00?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80\" alt=\"SUV\">\n                    <div class=\"car-card-content\">\n                        <h3>The Apex Explorer</h3>\n                        <p>Conquer any terrain with sophisticated style and robust capability.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-us\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Apex Motors</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-us-content\">\n                <p>Founded on a passion for automotive artistry, Apex Motors is dedicated to sourcing and presenting the finest luxury and performance vehicles. We believe that owning a car is more than transportation; it's an expression of taste, ambition, and freedom. Our commitment to quality, transparency, and exceptional customer service sets us apart.</p>\n                <p>From iconic classics to the latest supercars, each vehicle in our collection undergoes meticulous inspection. We invite you to experience the Apex difference.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form>\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"cta-button\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Motors. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}